title: eMedia Singing For Dummies v2
description: System Requirements : Windows 11, Windows 10, Windows 8, Windows 7, Windows Vista, Windows XP or macOS 10.5 to 10.14 (not compatible with 10.15 Catalina or later). If you purchased your eMedia software on or after September 7, 2019, upon receiving proof of purchase eMedia Music will provide you with a free upgrade to a macOS 10.15 (Catalina)-compatible version of an eMedia application when it becomes available. All other registered owners of eMedia software will be qualified for discounted upgrades.
